# Repo boundaries (roadmap)

This repo owns **ecosystem planning, agent-kit, and coordination docs**.

## Owns

- Master plan, PH-* work packages, ecosystem standards
- `agent-kit/` shared Cursor rules/hooks
- `scripts/install-agent-kit.sh`, `install-repo-boundaries.sh`, `local-org-cleanup.sh`

## Never add here

- Compiler implementation → **lic**
- Benchmark ingest/dashboard → **benchmarks**
- Proof UI → **proof-library**

## Cross-repo

- Changes that affect all repos go through agent-kit version bumps and per-repo install scripts.
